    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&quot;Neon. Door. Neon. Door. Neon. Door.&quot;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe you know this place. Maybe you've seen it before. Maybe every place actually exists in the screen, now, and it's just as good as going there. <strong>Exactly the same</strong>, in fact. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/8a581d939020f4ce48e7fd7c8b8c466d.poster.avif?t=1769502791\" width=1170 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/8a581d939020f4ce48e7fd7c8b8c466d.webm?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/8a581d939020f4ce48e7fd7c8b8c466d.mp4?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LIFE AT LFVCR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our warehouse features ultramodern personal computing and classic analog entertainment systems, familiar and foreign: <strong>landline phones, spinning wheels, hydraulic set changers, Milwaukee pachinko, and more.</strong> A home-away-from-home, scattered with <strong>books, posters, boxes, bottles, and VHS tapes</strong>. At Lightning Fast, you're family™.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2d8b006f7b627fe512905ca16edfdfdd.poster.avif?t=1769502791\" width=1170 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2d8b006f7b627fe512905ca16edfdfdd.webm?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2d8b006f7b627fe512905ca16edfdfdd.mp4?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hypercassette Tape Systems provided courtesy of SPAR Heavy Electric.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COP FROM THE FUTURE OF SPACE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I THINK THESE VHS TAPES ARE HAUNTED DUDE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/e7d31bdb66ca26817faa9b1166b2a6d6.poster.avif?t=1769502791\" width=1170 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/e7d31bdb66ca26817faa9b1166b2a6d6.webm?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/e7d31bdb66ca26817faa9b1166b2a6d6.mp4?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE COLD RUSHES IN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A murmur of something - <strong>signal, voice, mechanical or electronic maybe, music, repeating</strong> - lifts above the static, just for a moment. Pause. Turn. Try again, you can find it. Just try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2e2c1bd99c60b3676147fd4a0f308091.poster.avif?t=1769502791\" width=1170 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2e2c1bd99c60b3676147fd4a0f308091.webm?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344680/extras/2e2c1bd99c60b3676147fd4a0f308091.mp4?t=1769502791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
